rComments: I really enjoyed my class with Rupaleem. She is intelligent and thoughtful. The assignments helped to prepare me for a career in social work. She is committed to her students learning and to social justice - pretty great combination.
Clearly she is a smart and strong woman, which can be intimidating. Amazing prof!
